      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and offers a practical choice for those seeking a functional car at a reasonable price point. The exterior has noticeable cosmetic wear, including several scratches and minor dings consistent with its age. Inside, the cabin shows clear signs of use with some staining on the upholstery and minor wear on the control surfaces. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, though it may benefit from some upcoming maintenance to address minor leaks and suspension noise. It is a reliable daily driver for someone who prioritizes utility over aesthetics.",
