      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that's ready for its next adventure? I'm parting ways with my trusty car, and it has been such a joy to own. It's in really solid shape, runs like a dream, and has been well-loved throughout its life. Whether you're heading to work or planning a weekend getaway, this beauty is ready to hit the road with you. Come take it for a spin\u2014I'm sure you'll love it as much as I have!",
      "price": 34500.0,
