      "timestep_posted": 25
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sorted E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six power plant. This high-revving mill utilizes six individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing to produce a linear power band peaking at an 8,000 RPM redline. The Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission offers precise shift gates, delivering power to the rear wheels via the M Variable Differential Lock. Preventive maintenance is extensive: the rear subframe has been reinforced to mitigate floor pan fatigue, and the rod bearings have been replaced to ensure long-term bottom-end reliability. Suspension remains taut with refreshed bushings and dampers, maintaining the chassis's signature neutral balance. While the exterior shows minor road patina, the mechanical synchronization and drivetrain integrity remain exceptional for a driver-focused example.",
      "price": 38500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 25
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
